<html lang="en">

  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <script src="https://accounts.google.com/gsi/client" async defer></script>
    <script src="../JavaScript/teacherLogin.js" defer></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/teacherLogin.css" />
    <title>선생님용 로그인 페이지</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1 class="title">SIGN-IN</h1>
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>SIGN-IN</h2>
      <p>대시보드를 관리하려면 로그인을 해주세요</p>
      <form action="/teacherLogin" method="POST" class="container">
        <input type="text" name="teacher_id" id="teacher_id" placeholder="이름을 입력해주세요" autofocus required maxlength="5" pattern="{5}" />
        <input type="password" name="teacher_pw" id="teacher_pw" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력해주세요" autofocus required maxlength="50" pattern="[a-zA-Z0-9*@#]*" />
        <button type="submit">Sign in</button>
      </form>
      <div class="blueContainer"></div>
    </div>
  </body>

</html>